\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Q=\rho\oint_{A}^{B}v_{n}dl=\rho\oint_{A}^{B}\left(-v_{y}dx+v_{x}dy\right)=\rho\oint_{A}^{B}d\psi
\]

\end_inset

de manera que
